cdt_name:
- conda
channel_sources:

channel_targets:
- conda-forge main
cran_mirror:
- https://cran.r-project.org
docker_image:
- quay.io/condaforge/linux-anvil-x86_64:alma9
pin_run_as_build:
  r-base:
    min_pin: x.x
    max_pin: x.x
r_base:
- '4.4'

- linux-64

about.summary: Converts the United States Census geographic code for city, state (FIP and ICP), region, and birthplace, into the name of the region. e.g. takes an input of Census city code 5330 to it's actual city, Philadelphia. Will return NA for code that doesn't correspond to real location.

Converts the United States Census geographic code for city, state (FIP and ICP), region, and birthplace, into the name of the region. e.g. takes an input of Census city code 5330 to it's actual city, Philadelphia. Will return NA for code that doesn't correspond to real location.

name: r-censusgeography
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.1.0' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-censusgeography
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/censusGeography_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/censusGeography/censusGeography_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 2d5044073f36bbf32f1cb934b31644a02ef17a2f97bce0f778e1145a0b688fd9

build:
  number: 4
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-qdaptools
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-qdaptools

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('censusGeography')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('censusGeography')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=censusGeography
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Converts the United States Census geographic code for city, state (FIP and ICP), region,
    and birthplace, into the name of the region. e.g. takes an input of Census city
    code 5330 to it's actual city, Philadelphia. Will return NA for code that doesn't
    correspond to real location.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - izahn
